    <!-- Chosen Palette: Professional Blue & Clean Neutrals -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The application is designed as a conversion-focused landing page. The user flow is structured to build trust and provide value upfront. It begins with a hero section establishing credibility, followed by a section highlighting industry specializations (Medical, Dental, etc.) to resonate with target clients. The core is an interactive quote calculator that offers immediate, tangible value. This is supported by a "Why Choose Us" section for reinforcement, and concludes with a clear call-to-action‚Äîan integrated enquiry form. This structure was chosen to guide the user from initial interest to a qualified lead in a single, seamless experience. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Business Intro -> Goal: Inform/Trust -> Method: Hero section text with key stats -> Interaction: None -> Justification: Quickly establishes professionalism and core value propositions.
        - Specializations -> Goal: Connect -> Method: Thematic cards with icons (HTML/Tailwind) -> Interaction: None -> Justification: Visually communicates expertise in target sectors, making the service feel more relevant to the viewer.
        - Service List -> Goal: Engage/Inform -> Method: Interactive selectable cards -> Interaction: Click-to-select, visual state change -> Justification: Engages the user and allows them to customize their plan, feeding directly into the calculator.
        - Quote Estimate -> Goal: Convert -> Method: Dynamic text display updated by JS -> Interaction: Real-time update based on user input -> Justification: Provides instant, personalized value, which is a powerful incentive for making contact.
        - Enquiry Form -> Goal: Capture Lead -> Method: HTML form -> Interaction: On submit, JS constructs and opens a pre-filled mailto link -> Justification: A low-friction way to capture leads directly from the page without server-side code.
        - Library/Method: Vanilla JavaScript for all logic. No charts needed.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
